## Key techniques used here

| Technique | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `@WebMvcTest` | Load only the controller + MVC layer (fast slice). |
| `@Import(GlobalExceptionHandler.class)` | Test the real error-mapping advice. |
| `@MockitoBean` | Replace the service so only HTTP behaviour is tested. |
| `MockMvc` + `jsonPath` | Drive requests and assert on the JSON response body. |
| `header().string("Location", ...)` | Verify REST creation headers. |
| `given(...).willThrow(...)` (BDDMockito) | Simulate service errors to test status mapping. |
